# Delphi Build Output
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Win32/
Win64/
__history/
__recovery/
__DCU_CACHE/
*.dcu
*.exe
*.dll
*.bpl
*.dcp
*.so
*.apk
*.drc
*.map
*.dres
*.rsm
*.tds
*.dcu
*.lib
*.a
*.o
*.ocx

